import React from 'react';

export default ({
  Html,
  Head,
  Body,
  children,
  state: { siteData, renderMeta },
}) => (
  <Html lang="en-US">
    <Head>
      <meta charSet="UTF-8" />
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
      <title>Lagier & Lagier - web development and full-stack consulting</title>
      <meta name="description" content="Lagier & Lagier is a consulting agency for full-stack Javascript applications. We're here to clean up your code, implement a tough new feature, or advise on best practices to scale to the next level of your business." />
    </Head>
    <Body>{children}</Body>
  </Html>
)
